dct_title_s: Sectional map of the surveyed portion of Minnesota and the northwestern part of Wisconsin
dct_description_sm: Hand colored."Entered according to Act of Congress in the year 1857, by J.S. Sewall, in the Clerk's Office of the District Court for the Southern District of Minnesota."Includes view of Fuller House, St. Paul and advertisements for Caldwell, Whitney & Co., bankers, St. Paul and Henry Mckenty, realtor, St. Paul. Dimensions: 55 x 39 centimeters
